{
  "page": "Paymaster",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Paymaster</b> is a high ranking position within the <a href=\"/index.php/Mercenary#Free_Companies\" title=\"Mercenary\">free companies</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>. The paymaster is in charge with the accounting, drawing up contracts, collecting wages, dividing resources to ensure provisions, and payments of the company.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_paymasters\">Known paymasters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Paymaster&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known paymasters\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Tybero_Istarion\" title=\"Tybero Istarion\">Tybero Istarion</a>, of the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Sons\" title=\"Second Sons\">Second Sons</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Harry_Strickland\" title=\"Harry Strickland\">Harry Strickland</a>, former paymaster of the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a>, now the <a href=\"/index.php/Captain-general\" title=\"Captain-general\">captain-general</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gorys_Edoryen\" title=\"Gorys Edoryen\">Gorys Edoryen</a>, current paymaster of the Golden Company<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hugh_Hungerford\" title=\"Hugh Hungerford\">Hugh Hungerford</a>, former paymaster of the <a href=\"/index.php/Windblown\" title=\"Windblown\">Windblown</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Paymaster&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_treasurer\" title=\"Lord treasurer\">Lord treasurer</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_coin\" title=\"Master of coin\">Master of coin</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Paymaster&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_66\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 66\">Chapter 66</a>, Tyrion XII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-back